%header#header
  %div#logo-group
    %span#logo
      =image_tag 'bki_logo.png'

  %span#extr-page-header-space
    %span.hidden-mobile.hiddex-xs
      Need an account?
    %a.btn.btn-danger{ "href" => "register.html" }
      Create account

%div#main{ "role" => "main" }
  %div#content.container
    %div.row
      %div.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-7.col-lg-8.hidden-xs.hidden-sm
        %h1.txt-color-red.login-header-big
          BKI Systems
        %div.hero
          %div.pull-left.login-desc-box-l
            %h4.paragraph-header
              Get connected to your account anywhere you go.
            %div.login-app-icons
              %a.btn.btn-danger.btn-sm{ "href" => "javascript:void(0);" }
                Find out more

        %div.row
          %div.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.col-lg-6
            %h5.about-heading
              About SmartAdmin - Are you up to date?
            %p
              Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa.
          %div.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.col-lg-6
            %h5.about-heading
              Not just your average template!
            %p
              Et harum quidem rerum facilis est et expedita distinctio. Nam libero tempore, cum soluta nobis est eligendi voluptatem accusantium!
      %div.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-5.col-lg-4
        %div.well.no-padding
          %form.login-form.smart-form.client-form{ "action" => "index.html" }
            %header
              Sign In
            %fieldset
              %section
                %label.label
                  E-mail
                %label.input
                  %i.icon-append.fa.fa-user
                  %input{ "type" => "email", "name" => "email" }
                  %b.tooltip.tooltip-top-right
                    %i.fa.fa-user.txt-color-teal
                    Please enter email address/username
              %section
                %label.label
                  Password
                %label.input
                  %i.icon-append.fa.fa-lock
                  %input{ "type" => "password", "name" => "password" }
                  %b.tooltip.tooltip-top-right
                  %i.fa.fa-lock.txt-color-teal
                  Enter your password 
                %div.note
                  %a{ "href" => "forgotpassword.html" }
                    Forgot password?
              %section
                %label.checkbox
                  %input{ "type" => "checkbox", "name" => "remember", "checked" => "" }
                  %i
                  Stay signed in
            %footer
              %button.btn.btn-primary{ "type" => "submit" }
                Sign in

        %h5.text-center
          Or sign in using
          %ul.list-inline.text-center
            %li
              %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-circle{ "href" => "javascript:void(0);" }
                %i.fa.fa-facebook
            %li
              %a.btn.btn-info.btn-circle{ "href" => "javascript:void(0);" }
                %i.fa.fa-twitter


